## OSM-Derived Data

The files under `campus_scenarios/` and `subway_station_scenarios/` include
OpenStreetMap extracts and scenario YAML files derived from OpenStreetMap data.
OpenStreetMap data is available under the Open Data Commons Open Database
License (ODbL) 1.0.

When using or redistributing these data files, you must comply with the ODbL
terms, including attribution to OpenStreetMap contributors. The ODbL license is
available at:

https://opendatacommons.org/licenses/odbl/1-0/

## Third-Party Dependencies

External Python packages listed in `requirements.txt` are distributed under
their own licenses. This repository does not relicense those dependencies.
